#: /home/minds3t/omnipkg/src/omnipkg/cli.py:359
msgid "     we average ~60% savings, but less for C extensions/binaries)"
msgstr "우리는 평균 ~ 60% 절감 효과이지만 C 확장/바이너리의 경우 적습니다)"

#: /home/minds3t/omnipkg/src/omnipkg/cli.py:361
msgid "🤯 What makes this impossible with traditional tools:"
msgstr "🤯 전통적인 도구로 이것을 불가능하게 만드는 것 :"

#: /home/minds3t/omnipkg/src/omnipkg/cli.py:363
msgid "   • Switching versions requires environment restart"
msgstr "• 스위칭 버전에는 환경이 다시 시작되어야합니다"

#: /home/minds3t/omnipkg/src/omnipkg/cli.py:364
